                <p>I spent a large amount of the first week scaffolding the site. Due to being the sole creator of the wireframe diagrams in our documentation - based off of the descriptions provided by our group, I felt a drive to be the one to put them into practice. I spent a majority of my first week developing, building, maintaining, and updating the formatting to accomodate Lori's gameplay and Gabriel's leaderboard.</p>
                <p>To allow for easy access to multiple "pages" without redirecting to different pages, I created 3 toggleable divs called [gameplay], [leaderboard], and [game-over]. These "pages" contain the necessary content elements to support all of our site goals:</p>
