                    <li>[Gameplay] acts as both a start menu and the page on which the game is played.</li>
                    <li>[Leaderboard] exists to display both the player's score as well as the global top 16 scores.</li>
                    <li>[Game Over] display's the player's score from the completed game and allows them to submit their score to the global leaderboards.</li>
